data.description: Contract Pending On the market for backup offers. What and exceptional property?!?! This home is updated, well maintained and ready for you to call yours. So many updates, features and upgrades to list here so make sure you check out the attached document. Cul-de-sac street and walk through your backyard gate to arrive at the neighborhood playground and walking trail. Grade "A" Millard Schools and interstate access is less than 3 minuets from your front door. New interior paint, newer carpet, newer granite counter tops in the kitchen, double vanity in the primary bathroom and the basement was remodeled with-in the past 5 years. Pool upgrades and so much more! This home and the neighborhood are definite winners!AMA and taken from Sarpy County assessors website. SELLER IS RELATED TO THE LISTING AGENT.
